ZH: 1. 他必须使出全力才能完成这项任务。
EN: He must exert all his strength to complete this task.
ZH: 2. 她使出浑身解数来打动评委。
EN: She used all her tricks to impress the judges.
ZH: 3. 为了赢得比赛，他使出了最后一招。
EN: In order to win the game, he used his last move.
ZH: 4. 这个拼图太难了，我必须使出智慧来解决。
EN: This puzzle is too difficult, I have to use my intelligence to solve it.
ZH: 5. 尽管累得喘不过气，他还是使出力气继续跑步。
EN: Despite being out of breath from exhaustion, he continued running with all his strength.
ZH: 6. 为了成功，你必须使出自己的全部潜力。
EN: To succeed, you must utilize all your potential.
ZH: 7. 他必须使出忍耐力来面对挑战。
EN: He must use his patience to face the challenges.
ZH: 8. 她使出所能想到的一切方法来安慰我。
EN: She used every method she could think of to comfort me.
ZH: 9. 面对对手，他使出了出其不意的攻击方式。
EN: Faced with the opponent, he used unexpected attack methods.
ZH: 10. 为了保护自己，她使出夺命一击。
EN: To protect herself, she used a deadly blow.
ZH: 11. 他不得已使出了恳求的眼神。
EN: He had no choice but to use a pleading look.
ZH: 12. 这项任务如此复杂，我们只能使出全员共同合作的策略。
EN: The task is so complicated that we can only use a strategy of collective cooperation.
ZH: 13. 为了拯救人质，警察使出了特殊的战术。
EN: To rescue the hostages, the police used special tactics.
ZH: 14. 他使出音乐才华来打动观众的心。
EN: He used his musical talent to touch the hearts of the audience.
ZH: 15. 面对危险，他使出勇敢无畏的精神。
EN: Faced with danger, he used a brave and fearless spirit.
ZH: 16. 她使出所有的努力来帮助别人。
EN: She put in all her effort to help others.
ZH: 17. 虽然困难重重，但是他使出了毅力，成功地完成了任务。
EN: Despite the difficulties, he used his perseverance to successfully complete the task.
ZH: 18. 他使出最后一丝力气，终于拔出了卡住的钥匙。
EN: He used his last ounce of strength to finally pull out the stuck key.
ZH: 19. 受伤后，他依然使出最大的努力来完成训练。
EN: Even after being injured, he still made the biggest effort to complete the training.
ZH: 20. 老板使出了连续10个小时的努力来确保项目成功。
EN: The boss made a continuous 10-hour effort to ensure the success of the project.
